				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think the new UI is very abusable. I mean, should a Human w/out a coldstone/lightsone be able to see in the dark?<BR>
<BR>
No, but with the new UI, and the /wincolor options, one can easily  change the color of, say, the buffs window, enlarge it to cover the whole screen, and it would give those with poor night vision a perfect view of the night terrain. I use this a lot, so don't think i'm complaining. i just think it makes dark areas less dangerous, and easier to navigate through.<BR>
<BR>
/wincolor BUFF 0 0 150 2 works well.
