			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, trying to make it simple<BR>
<BR>
UI = User Interface.  It is how the buttons are laid out, what all you see in menus, etc.<BR>
<BR>
The big change:  If you play in full screen mode (the one without the box-like frame) all of the overlays (such as the chatbox, the list of people in your group, the health bars, etc.) can be moved to anywhere on the screen you want them.  In addition, when you access your inventory, it is just another transparent overlay, so you never have to go into the box-frame screen.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
